1. Cessation of compounding
:SKRSLUT.
:SWISS8.
.sp 3mm
&BANKNAVN. may at any time decide to cease compounding of non-performing
loans and credits, administratively and financially.
.sp 3mm
.kp off
.kp on
If compounding is ceased, and this has not been agreed with you, it does
not mean that &BANKNAVN. waives its right to receive interest of its claims
and to have any subsequent expenses covered. This applies, even if it
appears from a statement of account etc. that compounding has been ceased.
.sp 5mm
.kp off
.kp on
:SWISS10.
:FED.
2. Adjustment of payment
:SKRSLUT.
:SWISS8.
.sp 3mm
On change of interest and expenses, &BANKNAVN. is entitled to adjust the
payments as to size, number and frequency, or a combination thereof.
heraf.
.sp 5mm
.kp off
.kp on
:SWISS10.
:FED.
3. Information on financial conditions
:SKRSLUT.
:SWISS8.
.sp 3mm
You are obliged to keep &BANKNAVN. informed about your financial conditions
and, on request, deliver financial information.
.sp 5mm
.kp off
.kp on
:SWISS10.
:FED.
4. Termination and repayment
:SKRSLUT.
:SWISS8.
.sp 3mm
&BANKNAVN. is entitled to terminate any loans and credits, fully or partly,
without notice, and request payment of the amount due, including accrued
interest and expenses.
.sp 3mm
.kp off
.kp on
In such cases you have the right to receive a factual explanation
from &BANKNAVN..
.sp 3mm
.kp off
.kp on
You can, at any time, discharge your obligations, fully or partly,
according to the loan and credit agreement, unless otherwise agreed.
.sp 5mm
.kp off
.kp on
:SWISS10.
:FED.
5. Default or other reasons for expiry
:SKRSLUT.
:SWISS8.
.sp 3mm
In the following situations (which is not a complete list), it must be
expected that &BANKNAVN. will make use of its right to terminate loans and
credits without notice and require immediate payment of all debts.
.br
.kp off
.kp on
.of 5mm
a. ¤ If payments, interest, commission or instalments are not paid on due
date. This also applies for credits if you overdraw your credit limit
without the permission of &BANKNAVN..
.of
.br
.kp off
.kp on
.of 5mm
b. ¤ If you are subject to individual legal action in the nature of
execution or pre-trial attachment.
.of
.br
.kp off
.kp on
.of 5mm
c. ¤ If you are caught in reconstruction or bankruptcy proceedings or open
a debt settlement case.
.of
.br
.kp off
.kp on
.of 5mm
d. ¤ If you pass away.
.of
.br
.kp off
.kp on
.of 5mm
e. ¤ If you settle abroad, move your registered address
to a foreign country or move essential activities abroad and no
agreement exist as to the future repayment of loan/credits.
.of
.br
.kp off
.kp on
.of 5mm
f. ¤ If you have provided &BANKNAVN. with misleading information essential
to the establishment of the loan/credit.
.of
.br
.kp off
.kp on
.of 5mm
g. ¤ If you, no later than 14 days after preparation, do not deliver
annual report/accounts, statement of financial position, in so far as
personal operated establishments are concerned, and any other financial
information required by &BANKNAVN..
.of
.br
.kp off
.kp on
.of 5mm
h. ¤ If you do not keep &BANKNAVN. informed about your financial
conditions.
.of
.br
.kp off
.kp on
.of 5mm
i. ¤ If your creditworthiness is weakened.
.of
.br
.kp off
.kp on
