k. ¤ If pledged/mortgaged effects are sold without prior consent of
&BANKNAVN..
.of
.br
.kp off
.kp on
.of 5mm
l. ¤ If pledged/mortgaged boat, car, other movables or real property
is/are not properly insured or, on request, you omit to provide
documentation thereof.
.of
.br
.kp off
.kp on
.of 5mm
m. ¤ If you, without prior consent of &BANKNAVN., pay extraordinary
