Specifically about surety
:SKRSLUT.
:SWISS8.
.sp 3mm
.kp off
.kp on
:SWISS10.
:FED.
1. Extent of surety
:SKRSLUT.
:SWISS8.
.sp 3mm
The third party guarantor is held liable for your obligations towards
&BANKNAVN., including interest and other minor debt services.
.sp 5mm
.kp off
.kp on
:SWISS10.
:FED.
2. Reversal
:SKRSLUT.
:SWISS8.
.sp 3mm
If the loan/credit is repaid, fully or partly, and the payment or
additional security is set aside at a later point in time, the surety will
be maintained, whether you, or &BANKNAVN., have notified the third party
guarantor of the repayment or not.
.sp 5mm
.kp off
.kp on
:SWISS10.
:FED.
3. Use of payments
:SKRSLUT.
:SWISS8.
.sp 3mm
Payments from third party guarantors are first of all used in settlement of
interest, commission and expenses, secondly in settlement of other debt
secured by the third party guarantor.
.sp 3mm
.kp off
.kp on
If the loan/credit is not fully secured by surety, the payments are first
of all used in settlement of the unsecured part of the debt.
.sp 5mm
.kp off
.kp on
:SWISS10.
:FED.
4. Respite
:SKRSLUT.
:SWISS8.
.sp 3mm
 
Without consent of third party guarantor, &BANKNAVN. may grant a respite as
to payment of instalments, interest and other expenses, however, with
deference to article 47 of the Danish Financial Business Act.
.sp 5mm
.kp off
.kp on
:SWISS10.
:FED.
5. Voting right at creditors' meetings
:SKRSLUT.
:SWISS8.
.sp 3mm
At any creditors' meeting regarding you, &BANKNAVN. will exercise the
voting right connected to the object of the surety. This applies until
&BANKNAVN. has obtained full and irrefutable settlement of his or her
claims.
.sp 5mm
.kp off
.kp on
:SWISS10.
:FED.
6. Inter-surety and other securities
:SKRSLUT.
:SWISS8.
.sp 3mm
&BANKNAVN. reserves its right to realise any securities applied by you or
third party and to write off the revenue at &BANKNAVN.'s option. The third
party guarantor has no right of recourse in such securities.
.sp 3mm
.kp off
.kp on
This implies, among other things:
.sp 3mm
.of 3mm
* ¤ that &BANKNAVN. without the permission of the third party guarantor may
release other securities in relation to the obligation in question.
.of
.br
.of 3mm
* ¤ that &BANKNAVN. may use pledge/mortgage, which at the same time serves
as security against other claims but the obligation in question, in prior
recovery of such claims.
.of
.sp 5mm
.kp off
.kp on
:SWISS10.
:FED.
7. Notification right and right to dividend upon your liquidation
:SKRSLUT.
:SWISS8.
.sp 3mm
If the third party guarantor has to discharge your obligations towards
&BANKNAVN., &BANKNAVN. has notification right and right to dividend of the
amount paid in your estate.
.sp 5mm
.kp off
.kp on
:SWISS10.
:FED.
8. Enforcement
:SKRSLUT.
:SWISS8.
.sp 3mm
If the surety serves as security against loan, the loan instrument with
deed of indemnity may serve as basis for enforcement with the third party
guarantor according to article 478, section 1, paragraph 5 of the Danish
Administration of Justice Act.
.kp off
.tp 3mm
:SWISS8.
