:SWISS12.
:FED.
Specifically about pledge/mortgage
:SKRSLUT.
:SWISS8.
.sp 3mm
If the loan/credit is secured, the following provisions do also apply:
.sp 3mm
.kp off
.kp on
:SWISS10.
:FED.
1. Extent of the security
:SKRSLUT.
:SWISS8.
.sp 3mm
Pledge/mortgage serves as security for payment of
funds, interest, commission, legal costs and other expenses incurred in
connection with recovery of debt.
.sp 3mm
.kp off
.kp on
Pledge/mortgage applied by you serves as security for any obligation you
have or may have in the future towards &BANKNAVN.. &BANKNAVN. has a free
choice of which part of the consolidated credit balance, or which credit
balance out of two or more, must be reduced by means of the
pledge/mortgage.
.sp 5mm
.kp off
.kp on
:SWISS10.
:FED.
2. Insurance of pledged/mortgaged effects
:SKRSLUT.
:SWISS8.
.sp 3mm
If &BANKNAVN. has pledge/mortgage on car, boat, other movables or real
property, the pledger is obliged to take out a comprehensive motor and/or
fire insurance covering the pledged/mortgaged effects.
.sp 3mm
.kp off
.kp on
If the pledge/mortgage is applied by third party, you are obliged to pay
the insurance premium, if not paid by third party.
.sp 5mm
.kp off
.kp on
:SWISS10.
:FED.
3. Depreciation of pledge/mortgage
:SKRSLUT.
:SWISS8.
.sp 3mm
If the value of the pledge/mortgage is depreciated considerably, &BANKNAVN.
may require that you either extraordinarily reduce your debt/credit limit
or that additional funding is made available corresponding to the actual
depreciation. Otherwise, &BANKNAVN. may consider the loan/credit
non-performing.
.sp 3mm
.kp off
.kp on
However, if &BANKNAVN. has mortgage on real property which serves as your
permanent residence, &BANKNAVN. will not require any extraordinary
settlement in case the property value is depreciated, or other security
unless the depreciation is due to mismanagement.
.sp 5mm
.kp off
.kp on
:SWISS10.
:FED.
4. &BANKNAVN.'s right to pledged/mortgaged effects
:SKRSLUT.
:SWISS8.
.sp 3mm
&BANKNAVN. may use all pledgers' rights to pledged/mortgaged effects,
including receiving and confirming the receipt of any amount according to
the pledged/mortgaged effects, terminating and collecting, signing and
transferring pledged claims and mortgaging deeds to the bank or others, and
withdrawing amounts from pledged deposit accounts.
.sp 3mm
.kp off
.kp on
On pledging of shares etc., &BANKNAVN. may exercise all shareholders'
rights according to current company laws, articles of association, owner
agreements, if any, etc. However, the voting right lies with the pledger,
until &BANKNAVN. clearly notifies that the bank wants to make use of this
right.
.sp 3mm
.kp off
.kp on
If the pledge comprises insurance policies, the pledger is obliged, on
demand, to present &BANKNAVN. to proper receipt for timely payment of the
premium.
.sp 3mm
.kp off
.kp on
If &BANKNAVN. chooses to seek satisfaction in the buyback value of the
policy, &BANKNAVN. must be entitled to do so without having to await the
notice laid down in the national insurance contract law.
.sp 3mm
.kp off
.kp on
&BANKNAVN. is not obliged to seek cover in the applied pledge/mortgage in
advance, just as &BANKNAVN. has freedom of choice regarding use in relation
to the consolidated commitment.
.sp 5mm
.kp off
.kp on
:SWISS10.
:FED.
5. pledge/mortgage-related expenses
:SKRSLUT.
:SWISS8.
.sp 3mm
&BANKNAVN. may require payment of expenses for pledged/mortgaged effects.
.sp 5mm
.kp off
.kp on
&BANKNAVN. may also require coverage of &BANKNAVN.'s expenses in connection
with the handling of its interests as pledgee, including any costs in
connection with payment of insurance premium, inspection of the
pledged/mortgaged effects, costs in connection with legal advice, etc.
.sp 5mm
.kp off
.kp on
:SWISS10.
:FED.
6. Return of investment on the pledge/mortgage
:SKRSLUT.
:SWISS8.
.sp 3mm
Pledging/mortgaging comprises any interest and dividend of the
pledged/mortgaged effects, including bonus of life insurance policies, any
bonus shares and rights of shares, revenue of drawn bonds, rental, etc.
.sp 3mm
.kp off
.kp on
&BANKNAVN. is entitled, but not bound (neither in relation to third party
guarantors) to receive interest or dividend for payment of instalments,
interest and expenses.
.sp 5mm
.kp off
.kp on
:SWISS10.
:FED.
7. Notifications
:SKRSLUT.
:SWISS8.
.sp 3mm
The pledger is obliged to immediately forward all notifications he or she
receives of the pledged/mortgaged effects to &BANKNAVN..
.sp 5mm
.kp off
.kp on
:SWISS10.
:FED.
8. Drawing of bonds
:SKRSLUT.
:SWISS8.
.sp 3mm
If pledged bonds are drawn, and other bonds are bought instead of the drawn
bonds, &BANKNAVN. is entitled to register lien above these against VP
Securities A/S.
.sp 5mm
.kp off
.kp on
:SWISS10.
:FED.
9. Reversal
:SKRSLUT.
:SWISS8.
.sp 3mm
If the pledged/mortgaged-secured loan/credit is repaid, fully or partly,
and the payments are set aside at a later point in time, the pledger is
bound to establish the pledge of &BANKNAVN., whether &BANKNAVN. has
released the pledge or not.
.sp 5mm
.kp off
.kp on
:SWISS10.
:FED.
10. Respite
:SKRSLUT.
:SWISS8.
.sp 3mm
Without consent of pledger, &BANKNAVN. may grant a respite as to payment of
instalments, interest and other expenses.
.sp 5mm
.kp off
.kp on
:SWISS10.
:FED.
11. Enforcement
:SKRSLUT.
:SWISS8.
.sp 3mm
Any realisation of mortgage takes place after prior notice of the pledger
on transaction or otherwise, which &BANKNAVN. considers expedient,
including realisation on &BANKNAVN.'s own arrangement.
.sp 3mm
.kp off
.kp on
Prior to &BANKNAVN.'s sale of effects, a recommended letter is sent to the
pledger, in which the pledger, with 1 week's notice, is urged to fulfil the
requirements of &BANKNAVN..
.sp 3mm
.kp off
.kp on
However, this does not apply in case immediate sale is required, to avoid
or limit any loss.
.kp off

